## Pushing to GitHub

This repo uses the `github.com-danny` SSH alias. The remote must be:

```
git@github.com-danny:dannySubsense/<REPO-NAME>.git
```

If it gets set to `git@github.com:...` (the default alias, which resolves to majortom55), pushes will fail with "Repository not found". Fix with:

```bash
git remote set-url origin "git@github.com-danny:dannySubsense/<REPO-NAME>.git"
```
